long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Five Nights at Freddy’s (FNaF) is a renowned horror game series that immerses players in a spine-chilling and suspenseful experience. Developed by Scott Cawthon, the series revolves around night security guards tasked with surviving their shifts at various Freddy Fazbear’s Pizza locations, where animatronic characters come to life with a sinister intent. Navigate the eerie settings, monitor security cameras, and ensure your survival against the lurking animatronics.
